- connect one of the cassandra nodes as root user. example;

``` {.bash org-language="sh"}
cqlsh $CASS_HOST -u $ROOT_USER -p$ROOT_PASS
```

``` sql
CREATE ROLE username with password = 'password' AND LOGIN = true;
```

grant all permissions for all keyspaces

``` sql
GRANT ALL PERMISSIONS ON ALL KEYSPACES TO username;
```
